{"tid":329806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"說到外交衣著學，皇妃Kate Middleton每次都嬴幾條街。","createTime":"2017-07-20T16:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T18:28:49.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"250a023b91bb8d2fb3a1115a4023ae1f177f0b2a","tid":329806,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/000545_2484aec6dc4456298a0b137e3013178a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F000545_2484aec6dc4456298a0b137e3013178a.jpg&h=917b8257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法美第一夫人在巴黎世紀同場，美國第一夫人Melania Trump終於一洗貴婦外遊的外訪形象，選對了登得上大場面的衣著，不再成為格格不入的局外人。其實第一夫人們的衣著選擇可大有學問，選擇品牌上也有深層考慮，以平衡代表她們所屬的國家，又或向訪問國家以示友好的考量。例如法國第一夫人Brigitte Macron常以法國品牌Louis Vuitton示人，而Melania Trump到訪巴黎作客時，選擇當地具代表性品牌Dior與法國國旗配色，可是最直接而又大方得體的選擇。但要說到現今最懂得外交衣著（Diplomatic Dressing）的，必定非英國皇妃Kate Middleton莫屬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2gNnbiT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gNnbiT&d=H3R%2FOtjhShBos1YI6J9p%2BqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=cdc87fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2gNnbiT</a>"},{"pid":"c60a27f6cf5a3b52dd4a1039920c1a5afeb40e24","tid":329806,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T18:28:49.000Z","msg":"post晒出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}